Popular Nigerian singer, Peter Okoye aka Mr P has responded to Osaze Odemwingie after the footballer called him out.  It will be recalled that Osaze had called Peter out on social media recently. The retired professional footballer via his Instastories attacked Peter over his lottery business and also for organizing a dance challenge. In his post, Osaze accused Peter of robbing people via his lottery business. In a DM he sent to Osaze which he shared online, Peter said the footballer looked sick and needs help. Read his post below:  Source